Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
- SilverStripe 2.3 +
- TagField trunk

Documentation
-----------------------------------------------

Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
Install both TagField module and TaggerField Module

Usage Overview
-----------------------------------------------
This field extends the TagField, with a new API to add each tag
individually in a front-end form that using this field. The features
in TagField, like auto suggestion are maintained. The field initialises
a list of the current object's tags and by click on a "+" button, an input
field is displayed, text typed-in will be added to the existing tag list when 
key stroke "enter" or click-on the auto-suggested word. 


Known issues
-----------------------------------------------

Future works
-----------------------------------------------
Merge this with the older TagField so it works by setting an variable of the field configuration, such as "itemised", to be true..